#rain module by yvain douard, yvain29@gmail.com  

Experimental.
Strafing the index is good, effectiveness depends on the combination entropy/performance.
Even though the treated placeholder rotate, big chunks of initial characters will be present above a certain length.
So now you should limit the length to about 8 with lowercase set, untill I find a way to impact on the character selection as previously.
Don't forget to use -mask=?w...
